      "text": "and for the same reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 101000.0,
      "end_time": 102640.0,
      "text": "As Bloomberg puts it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 102640.0,
      "end_time": 105800.0,
      "text": "China is playing a 9 trillion dollar game of chicken"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 108110.0,
      "text": "called Shadow Banking."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 108110.0,
      "end_time": 109650.0,
      "text": "And like a game of chicken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 109650.0,
      "end_time": 112720.0,
      "text": "some investors will get out in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 112720.0,
      "end_time": 114620.0,
      "text": "But others will plunge off the cliff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 114620.0,
      "end_time": 118750.0,
      "text": "bursting into a ball of flames on the rocks below."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 118750.0,
      "end_time": 120320.0,
      "text": "So what is this totally legit"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 120320.0,
      "end_time": 123119.0,
      "text": "and trustworthy sounding “shadow banking”?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 123120.0,
      "end_time": 124300.0,
      "text": "To put it simply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 124300.0,
      "end_time": 125820.0,
      "text": "shadow banking is when banks—"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 125820.0,
      "end_time": 127470.0,
      "text": "or companies that are not banks—"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 127470.0,
      "end_time": 130109.0,
      "text": "lend money outside of the normal structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 130109.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131750.0,
      "text": "of bank deposits and loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 131750.0,
      "end_time": 134790.0,
      "text": "Here’s a simplified explanation."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 134790.0,
      "end_time": 136319.0,
      "text": "In the traditional banking system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 136319.0,
      "end_time": 138429.0,
      "text": "if a business owner wants to grow his business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 138430.0,
      "end_time": 141719.0,
      "text": "he goes to a bank, and that bank loans him money."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 141719.0,
      "end_time": 142719.0,
      "text": "Over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 142719.0,
      "end_time": 143829.0,
      "text": "he repays that money to the bank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 143829.0,
      "end_time": 144849.0,
      "text": "plus interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 144849.0,
      "end_time": 147780.0,
      "text": "Let’s say a single bank makes 100 loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 147780.0,
      "end_time": 150599.0,
      "text": "It’s pretty careful about who it loans to."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 150599.0,
      "end_time": 151599.0,
      "text": "But even so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 151599.0,
      "end_time": 153238.0,
      "text": "some of the businesses will fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 153239.0,
      "end_time": 155290.0,
      "text": "so Chinese regulations require"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 155290.0,
      "end_time": 156790.0,
      "text": "that the bank set aside money"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 156790.0,
      "end_time": 159459.0,
      "text": "to cover potential losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 159459.0,
      "end_time": 160790.0,
      "text": "But shadow banking operates"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 160790.0,
      "end_time": 162739.0,
      "text": "outside that traditional system."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 162739.0,
      "end_time": 165120.0,
      "text": "Let’s say 100 businesses want loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 165120.0,
      "end_time": 168230.0,
      "text": "A shadow bank packages those 100 potential loans"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 168230.0,
      "end_time": 171250.0,
      "text": "into what’s called a Wealth Management Product."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 171250.0,
      "end_time": 173129.0,
      "text": "Then it goes to investors and is like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 173129.0,
      "end_time": 175209.0,
      "text": "“Hey, buy our Wealth Management Product."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 175209.0,
      "end_time": 176939.0,
      "text": "It has a high interest rate.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 176939.0,
      "end_time": 178760.0,
      "text": "When the businesses repay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 178760.0,
      "end_time": 180668.0,
      "text": "the investors will get their investment back"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 180669.0,
      "end_time": 182400.0,
      "text": "plus a lot of interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 184209.0,
      "text": "This is shadow banking."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 184209.0,
      "end_time": 186370.0,
      "text": "It can also get more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 186370.0,
      "end_time": 188560.0,
      "text": "Because sometimes the bank isn’t a bank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 188560.0,
      "end_time": 189769.0,
      "text": "but just a regular company"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 189769.0,
      "end_time": 191959.0,
      "text": "that packages investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 191959.0,
      "end_time": 193249.0,
      "text": "And sometimes the businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 193249.0,
      "end_time": 194249.0,
      "text": "that want to borrow money"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 194249.0,
      "end_time": 195750.0,
      "text": "aren’t regular businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 195750.0,
      "end_time": 197769.0,
      "text": "They might even be a local government"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 197769.0,
      "end_time": 200599.0,
      "text": "that wants money to build a bridge or whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 200599.0,
      "end_time": 202108.0,
      "text": "All these things can be packaged"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 202109.0,
      "end_time": 203849.0,
      "text": "into Wealth Management Products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 203849.0,
      "end_time": 205980.0,
      "text": "or other types of financial products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 205980.0,
      "end_time": 207980.0,
      "text": "and then sold to investors—"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 207980.0,
      "end_time": 209659.0,
      "text": "or sold to investment companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 209659.0,
      "end_time": 211990.0,
      "text": "which then re-package them"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 211990.0,
      "end_time": 214488.0,
      "text": "before selling to individual investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 214489.0,
      "end_time": 215569.0,
      "text": "A lot of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 215569.0,
      "end_time": 217418.0,
      "text": "shadow bank loans get so complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 217419.0,
      "end_time": 218480.0,
      "text": "that no one understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 218480.0,
      "end_time": 220638.0,
      "text": "exactly what the risk is."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 220639.0,
      "end_time": 222110.0,
      "text": "According to this article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 222110.0,
      "end_time": 224840.0,
      "text": "“The repackaging of credit is so complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 224840.0,
      "end_time": 226579.0,
      "text": "that bankers often have to resort to"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 226579.0,
      "end_time": 228860.0,
      "text": "line drawings that look like schematic plans"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 228860.0,
      "end_time": 230739.0,
      "text": "for a Rube Goldberg device"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 230739.0,
      "end_time": 233559.0,
      "text": "to explain to clients what&#39;s going on.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 233559.0,
      "end_time": 235120.0,
      "text": "A Rube Goldberg device."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 236189.0,
      "text": "Like when you pull a lever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 236189.0,
      "end_time": 237918.0,
      "text": "that sets a wheel in motion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 237919.0,
      "end_time": 240309.0,
      "text": "that knocks down some dominoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 240309.0,
      "end_time": 243700.0,
      "text": "that ends up destroying the economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 243700.0,
      "end_time": 244939.0,
      "text": "But all this shadow banking"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 244939.0,
      "end_time": 246629.0,
      "text": "and Wealth Management whatevers"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 246629.0,
