      "text": "Give us your money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 273690.0,
      "end_time": 276440.0,
      "text": "and you’ll have sunshine in your heart!"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 276440.0,
      "end_time": 277440.0,
      "text": "That bank, Everbright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 277440.0,
      "end_time": 279730.0,
      "text": "is actually a legit commercial bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 279730.0,
      "end_time": 281590.0,
      "text": "It makes regular loans, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 281590.0,
      "end_time": 283190.0,
      "text": "But recently it’s also been selling"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 283190.0,
      "end_time": 286170.0,
      "text": "a lot of shadow banking products to investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 286170.0,
      "end_time": 287380.0,
      "text": "because that allows Everbright"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 287380.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "to maximize profit without putting"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291690.0,
      "text": "so much of its own money on the line."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 291690.0,
      "end_time": 294670.0,
      "text": "Basically, it sells the risk to investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 294670.0,
      "end_time": 296800.0,
      "text": "But a lot of Chinese investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
