      "text": "because the Chinese government will probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 299820.0,
      "end_time": 301810.0,
      "text": "bail everyone out if things go badly."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 301810.0,
      "end_time": 304630.0,
      "text": "Like this investor in this Bloomberg article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 304630.0,
      "end_time": 306350.0,
      "text": "who explains that the Chinese government"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 306350.0,
      "end_time": 309460.0,
      "text": "would never let a big wealth management product fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 309460.0,
      "end_time": 312810.0,
      "text": "because it’s just not Chinese culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 312810.0,
      "end_time": 314650.0,
      "text": "Sounds like wishful thinking, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 314650.0,
      "end_time": 315989.0,
      "text": "But the Chinese government has"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 315990.0,
      "end_time": 318120.0,
      "text": "bailed out banks in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 318120.0,
      "end_time": 322170.0,
      "text": "Like the $45 billion dollar bailout in 2004."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 322170.0,
      "end_time": 324980.0,
      "text": "So assuming they’ll do it again seems reasonable."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 324980.0,
      "end_time": 327440.0,
      "text": "Although if you’ve ever read the terms and conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 327440.0,
      "end_time": 329469.0,
      "text": "on any investment product ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 329470.0,
      "end_time": 331150.0,
      "text": "you’ve seen that “past performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 331150.0,
      "end_time": 333429.0,
      "text": "is no guarantee of future results.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 333430.0,
      "end_time": 335800.0,
      "text": "Sure, the Chinese government may have done"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 335800.0,
      "end_time": 339640.0,
      "text": "a small 45 billion dollar bailout in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 339640.0,
      "end_time": 343390.0,
      "text": "But it doesn’t want to do a 9 trillion dollar bailout now."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 343390.0,
      "end_time": 344640.0,
      "text": "Besides, back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 344640.0,
      "end_time": 347419.0,
      "text": "there was almost no shadow banking in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 347420.0,
      "end_time": 349560.0,
      "text": "It only started happening on a large scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 349560.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "after the global financial crisis ten years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 354970.0,
      "text": "Authorities tried to stimulate China’s economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 354970.0,
      "end_time": 357780.0,
      "text": "by having banks lend more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 357780.0,
      "end_time": 360250.0,
      "text": "But soon, demand for borrowing got so high"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 360250.0,
      "end_time": 363190.0,
      "text": "that banks didn’t have enough money to lend people."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 363190.0,
      "end_time": 364990.0,
      "text": "So banks started packaging loans"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 364990.0,
      "end_time": 367390.0,
      "text": "and selling them to investors to get the cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 367390.0,
      "end_time": 369409.0,
      "text": "And it became such a big market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 369410.0,
      "end_time": 370870.0,
      "text": "other companies that aren’t even banks"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 370870.0,
      "end_time": 372270.0,
      "text": "got into the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 372270.0,
      "end_time": 374969.0,
      "text": "According to a 2016 report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 374970.0,
      "end_time": 376120.0,
      "text": "shadow bank loans now make up"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 376120.0,
      "end_time": 379160.0,
      "text": "57 percent all loans in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 379160.0,
      "end_time": 380160.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 380160.0,
      "end_time": 382360.0,
      "text": "more than half of all lending in China now"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 382360.0,
      "end_time": 385900.0,
      "text": "is actually done through shadow banking!"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 385900.0,
      "end_time": 386340.0,
      "text": "And this is a big problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 386340.0,
      "end_time": 388250.0,
      "text": "because shadow bank loans are usually"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 388250.0,
      "end_time": 390890.0,
      "text": "a lot riskier than traditional loans."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 390890.0,
      "end_time": 392940.0,
      "text": "Once companies start packaging and repackaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 392940.0,
      "end_time": 397150.0,
      "text": "it’s easy to lose track of what the risk actually is."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 397150.0,
      "end_time": 399250.0,
      "text": "It even starts to seem like a good idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 399250.0,
      "end_time": 403210.0,
      "text": "like jumping out of a plane without a parachute."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 403210.0,
      "end_time": 404210.0,
      "text": "The problem is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 404210.0,
      "end_time": 407560.0,
      "text": "it only works if you’re you’re Keanu Reeves, dude."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 407560.0,
      "end_time": 410250.0,
      "text": "Oh, and there’s another problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 410250.0,
      "end_time": 412000.0,
      "text": "Shadow banking loans don’t get recorded"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 412000.0,
      "end_time": 413990.0,
      "text": "on banks’ balance sheets."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 413990.0,
      "end_time": 414990.0,
      "text": "That makes banks look"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 414990.0,
      "end_time": 416930.0,
      "text": "healthier than they actually are—"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 416930.0,
      "end_time": 419270.0,
      "text": "and that also increases the risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 419270.0,
      "end_time": 420270.0,
      "text": "And guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 420270.0,
      "end_time": 422799.0,
      "text": "That’s exactly what happened in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 422800.0,
      "end_time": 425740.0,
      "text": "leading up to the 2007 crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 425740.0,
      "end_time": 426740.0,
      "text": "Banks had been packaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 426740.0,
      "end_time": 428800.0,
      "text": "and repackaging home loans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 428800.0,
      "end_time": 431310.0,
      "text": "then selling and reselling the packages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 431310.0,
      "end_time": 433600.0,
      "text": "and eventually even the nerds at Lehman Brothers"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 433600.0,
      "end_time": 437170.0,
      "text": "had no idea how to calculate the risk anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 437170.0,
      "end_time": 439740.0,
      "text": "Shadow banking in the US was the lever"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 439740.0,
      "end_time": 442390.0,
      "text": "that set the global financial crisis in motion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 442390.0,
      "end_time": 444870.0,
      "text": "and ironically, its domino effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 444870.0,
      "end_time": 446110.0,
      "text": "is what led to the rise of"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 446110.0,
      "end_time": 448710.0,
      "text": "shadow banking in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 448710.0,
      "end_time": 450820.0,
      "text": "And now Chinese authorities are getting worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 450820.0,
      "end_time": 452930.0,
      "text": "about what’s coming next."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 452930.0,
      "end_time": 453930.0,
      "text": "In fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 453930.0,
      "end_time": 456460.0,
      "text": "“Zhou Xiaochuan, the head of China’s central bank"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 456460.0,
      "end_time": 458490.0,
      "text": "has openly warned that authorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 458500.0,
      "end_time": 459970.0,
      "text": "need to curb financial risks"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 459970.0,
      "end_time": 462390.0,
      "text": "that might lead to a ‘Minsky Moment’—"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 462390.0,
      "end_time": 464650.0,
      "text": "a sudden collapse of asset prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 464650.0,
      "end_time": 466400.0,
      "text": "sparked by debt or currency pressures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 468000.0,
      "text": "after a long period of growth.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 468680.0,
      "end_time": 471800.0,
      "text": "Basically, bad debt in shadow banking"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 471800.0,
      "end_time": 473800.0,
      "text": "could end up wrecking the Chinese economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 473800.0,
      "end_time": 475570.0,
      "text": "And if the Chinese economy gets wrecked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 475570.0,
      "end_time": 477500.0,
      "text": "it could lead to serious consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 477500.0,
      "end_time": 478960.0,
      "text": "for the Chinese Communist Party."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 478960.0,
      "end_time": 480130.0,
      "text": "You know, because no one"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 480130.0,
      "end_time": 482750.0,
      "text": "believes in that communism stuff anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 482750.0,
      "end_time": 484440.0,
      "text": "so they tell people to go make money"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 484440.0,
      "end_time": 486610.0,
      "text": "and don’t talk about politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 486610.0,
      "end_time": 487950.0,
      "text": "But if people start losing their money"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 487950.0,
      "end_time": 489460.0,
      "text": "on a massive scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 489460.0,
      "end_time": 492599.0,
      "text": "people might start talking about politics again—"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 492600.0,
      "end_time": 493980.0,
      "text": "like who’s to blame."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 493980.0,
      "end_time": 497100.0,
      "text": "That’s why, at a top level conference in July,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 497100.0,
      "end_time": 499430.0,
      "text": "Xi Jinping declared that financial security"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 499430.0,
      "end_time": 501870.0,
      "text": "was vital to national security."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 501870.0,
      "end_time": 504920.0,
      "text": "“National security” is of course code for the CCP"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 504920.0,
      "end_time": 507670.0,
      "text": "securing its power over the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 507670.0,
      "end_time": 509900.0,
      "text": "But it’s not 2007 anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 509900.0,
      "end_time": 511520.0,
      "text": "It’s 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 511520.0,
      "end_time": 513150.0,
      "text": "We have iPhone 10s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 513150.0,
      "end_time": 515630.0,
      "text": "Johnny Depp is a Harry Potter villain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 515630.0,
      "end_time": 517419.0,
      "text": "and Chinese shadow banking has swelled"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 517419.0,
      "end_time": 520590.0,
      "text": "to more than $9 trillion."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 520590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522380.00000000006,
      "text": "The Chinese government can’t afford"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 522380.0,
      "end_time": 523510.0,
      "text": "to bail everyone out"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 523510.0,
      "end_time": 524920.0,
      "text": "when things go south."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 527500.0,
      "text": "They’re trying to rein in shadow banking."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 527500.0,
      "end_time": 529620.0,
      "text": "But once you let the tiger out of the cage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 529620.0,
      "end_time": 530620.0,
      "text": "well, it..."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 530620.0,
      "end_time": 533620.0,
      "text": "I guess it runs around and eats people."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 533620.0,
      "end_time": 535930.0,
      "text": "So what do you think of China’s shadow banking?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 535930.0,
      "end_time": 537430.0,
      "text": "Leave your comments below."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 537430.0,
      "end_time": 539140.0,
      "text": "Once again I’m Matt Gnaizda."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 539140.0,
      "end_time": 541520.0,
      "text": "Now it’s time for that thing we do at the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 543760.0,
      "end_time": 544780.0,
      "text": "You’re still here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 544780.0,
      "end_time": 545500.0,
      "text": "Good."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 545500.0,
      "end_time": 546120.0,
      "text": "Don’t worry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 546120.0,
      "end_time": 548500.0,
      "text": "I haven’t taken over China Uncensored."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 548500.0,
      "end_time": 550200.0,
      "text": "Chris will be back soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 550200.0,
      "end_time": 551790.0,
      "text": "In the meantime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 551900.0,
      "end_time": 552900.0,
      "text": "if you like this show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 552900.0,
      "end_time": 553810.0,
      "text": "we hope you can click on this orange button"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 553810.0,
      "end_time": 555150.0,
      "text": "and support us by pledging"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 555150.0,
      "end_time": 557240.0,
      "text": "a dollar or more per episode."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 557240.0,
      "end_time": 559640.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll invest it in a Chinese wealth management product."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 560420.0,
      "end_time": 563160.0,
      "text": "Click to go to our fundraising website Patreon."
    }
  ]
}